    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Arcotheres vicajii (Chhapgar, 1957) comb. nov., A, female (CW 8.6 mm, CL 7.7 mm) (LFSC.ZRC-115), Mumbai, India; B, holotype, male (CW 3.7 mm, CL 3.7 mm) (ZSI-C3361/1), Mumbai, India. A, B, overall habitus. Scale bars = 1.0 mm." ;
