    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Arcotheres vicajii (Chhapgar, 1957) comb. nov., female (CW 8.6 mm, CL 7.7 mm) (LFSC.ZRC-115), Mumbai, India. A, carapace; B, right chela outer view; C, right chela inner view; D, pleon; E, frontal view; F, left MXP3. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
