    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Arcotheres vicajii (Chhapgar, 1957) comb. nov. Colour in life. A, ovigerous female (CW 8.0 mm, CL 6.7 mm) (ZRC 2018.0768), India; B, male (CW 4.5 mm, CL 4.2 mm) (ZRC 2018.0768), India." ;
