    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Arcotheres vicajii (Chhapgar, 1957) comb. nov., A–C, ovigerous female (CW 8.2 mm, CL 6.9 mm) (ZRC 2018.0768), India; D, non-ovigerous female (CW 8.0 mm, CL 6.7 mm) (ZRC 2018.0768), India; E, male (CW 4.5 mm, CL 4.2 mm) (ZRC 2018.0768), India.A, D, E, overall habitus; B, ventral view of cephalothorax; C, frontal view of cephalothorax" ;
